Ids.Id: Caenorhabditis elegans N2 larval L1 (lin-35) RNA library L1LIN35-1 array capture 1

Description.Title: Caenorhabditis elegans N2 larval L1 (lin-35) RNA library L1LIN35-1 array capture 1

Comment.Paragraph: Array capture experiment to remove messages already detected in other RNAseq experiments on C. elegans N2 larva L1 (lin-35) library. This sample is available through the modENCODE DCC (www.modencode.org) as: L1LIN35-1cap1 The original N2 larva L1 (lin-35) library is available as DCC project: lin-35(n745) larva mid-L1 25dC 4.0 hrs post-L1 Local library name: L1LIN35-1cap1 Quality values are ASCII encoded Phred + 33. Flowcell 428A0AAXX was processed with GAPipeline 1.4 and is 36bp. Flowcell 61BDCAAXX was processed with GAPipeline 1.8 and is 76bp.
